<section xmlns:ns0="http://www.w3.org/2001/XInclude">
  <num>21-104</num>
  <heading>Termination of guardianship of the person.</heading>
  <text>A natural guardianship or an appointive guardianship of the person of an infant ceases when said infant becomes 18 years of age or marries.</text>
